<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Dream1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Dream,</orth> subst. thought or vision in sleep: <bibl n="shak. son 129.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 129, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.45" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.45" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 45</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.157.45" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 157</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.239.45" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 239</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 5.4.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. V, 4, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.3.172" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 3, 172</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.142" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 142</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 2.2.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 2, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.184" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 2, 184</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.2.147" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 2, 147</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.26" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.2.22" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 22</bibl> etc. etc. <cit><quote>I have dreamt a fearful d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.212" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 V, 3, 212</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I dreamt a d. to-night,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 1.4.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 4, 50</bibl></cit>.<lb />Hence == idle fancy: <bibl n="shak. mm 4.1.64" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 1, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 2.2.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 2, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 2.5.211" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 5, 211</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.82" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 2, 82</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.4.346" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 4, 346</bibl>. <cit><quote>a d. of what thou wert,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.88" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 88</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.2.34" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 2, 34</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.2.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 2, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.578" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 578</bibl>. <cit><quote>if consequence do but approve my d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.64" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 64</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>